Less is more. 💡 Mark Sisson shares his approach to finding the minimum effective dose in fitness, nutrition, and life. 

It’s not about doing the most—it’s about doing just enough to maintain strength, resilience, and health without overdoing it.

How are you finding your sweet spot in training, eating, and living? Let us know in the comments!
